data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This home boasts 2 bedrooms 2 baths, pool and one car garage.  The property includes a pool, which is a valuable amenity in Florida's warm climate. While it may require current maintenance, it is the highlight of this home.  The home consists of a large backyard for relaxation and entertainment. It offers proximity to beaches, shopping, dining, and various amenities in the area. Ac was installed in 2018. Can Air Bnb. Buyer to verify pertinent information and measurements.  Approximately 10 minute drive to Indian Rocks Beach, Approx 5 minute drive to Largo mall for shopping and eating.
